snippet.title: Amber the Shade-Mistakes(formerly the aries for libra project)
snippet.description: Matt Abbott on guitar,Rob Negron on vocals and recorded by Vigo Cabrerra. This demo is the first of a bunch of songs Matt had stored in the depths of his writing vault, Rob heard them and began putting vocal melodies and lyrics to them. Matt Abbott is a gifted writer and his songs bring out the emotions that Rob unleashes in his singing. There will be a lot more coming, please enjoy,tell your friends and subscribe to Vigo Cabrerra  on youtube
